Class NotSteppableTile

java.lang.Object
com.game.Utilities.Position
com.game.Tile.Tile
com.game.Tile.NotSteppableTile
public class NotSteppableTile extends Tile
Represents a tile that cannot be stepped on by game entities. This tile does not mark the end of a game level.
